article.description: — Braeden Smith scored 17 points as Colgate beat Brown 72-70 in a season opener on Monday night.
article.headline: Braeden Smith scores 17 as Colgate downs Brown 72-70
article.linkText: Braeden Smith scores 17 as Colgate downs Brown 72-70
article.story: HAMILTON, N.Y. -- — Braeden Smith scored 17 points as Colgate beat Brown 72-70 in a season opener on Monday night. Smith added five assists and three steals for the Raiders. Nicolas Louis-Jacques added 15 points. Keegan Records had 14 points and six rebounds. Kino Lilly Jr. finished with 21 points for the Bears. Nana Owusu-Anane added 20 points, seven rebounds, three steals and three blocks for Brown. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
